### Phase 4: Animation & SEO ✅ ABGESCHLOSSEN
- [x] GSAP ScrollReveal + StaggerReveal
- [x] Framer Motion PageTransition
- [x] prefers-reduced-motion Fallbacks
- [x] JSON-LD (Organization + FAQPage)
